---
title: Crunchy Ranch Chicken with Roasted Green Beans & Buttery Baby Potatoes
description: With just five minutes of prep and a hands-free turn in the oven, you can get juicy chicken cutlets with a cheesy panko crust and garlicky green beans on the table with minimal fuss. A side of buttery, ranch-seasoned baby potatoes seals the deal. But the best part? Thanks to the oven-ready tray you'll find in your box, there’s practically no cleanup required.
